    <item>
      <title>智利财政部长在养老金谈判中表明立场更强硬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-s-finance-minister-signals-tougher-stance-in-pension-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利财政部长表示，智利政府将加强谈判策略，以在参议院批准加布里埃尔·博里奇总统的旗舰养老金改革，避免过早做出让许多盟友失望的让步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-s-finance-minister-signals-tougher-stance-in-pension-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 19:19:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯将就下周访问俄罗斯时对中国的支持发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/china-s-support-of-russian-war-machine-will-draw-blinken-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿安东尼·布林肯下周访华时将带来一项矛盾的使命：传达美国对中国企业支持俄罗斯战争机器的严重关切，同时确保与北京的关系不会再次脱轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/china-s-support-of-russian-war-machine-will-draw-blinken-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 18:12:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国众议院通过950亿美元援助乌克兰、以色列和台湾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/house-passes-taiwan-aid-bill-to-be-combined-with-ukraine-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周六通过了对乌克兰 610 亿美元的新援助，结束了长达六个月的政治僵局，在此期间基辅的库存因与俄罗斯的战争而减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/house-passes-taiwan-aid-bill-to-be-combined-with-ukraine-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利央行行长认为在全球风险中谨慎降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-central-bank-president-sees-rate-cuts-on-track-despite-global-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利央行行长罗莎娜·科斯塔(Rosanna Costa)表示，延长全球最大降息周期之一的计划保持不变，因为政策制定者已经将新的全球风险纳入其前景中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-central-bank-president-sees-rate-cuts-on-track-despite-global-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 16:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
